      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay cool. i saw online that some people say it might make you feel a bit more jittery or heart racing if you mix them, but i figured since st johns wort is just a plant it wouldn't be a huge deal compared to the actual meds? do you think i should be worried about that at all?",
